txt.en: Stay hidden and let events transpire
Make your way towards Borangos' inner sanctum in Nargroth.
With the knowledge you now hold, you must speak to Isnír at once!
Find a suitable place to hide.
Stay hidden and let events transpire.
Upon receiving the remnants of the ancient ward originally used to keep Borangos at bay, Isnír wishes for you to return to Nargroth in the hopes of learning more about the domain of Great Rogmul.
Borangos will not notice you here
Find a suitable place to hide
Make your way towards Borangos' inner sanctum in Nargroth
